commit.message:
fix performance bug in weak hash tables implementation

buckets were enlarged inefficiently (sz -> sz+3)
this is now replaced with (sz -> 3*sz/2 + 3), along the lines
of OCaml's Weak implementation

more tests are added (though they fail at showing a significant
difference)
